===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|mathematics}} the distance between two points located on a [[grid]], where the only path allowed is [[vertical]] and [[horizontal]] lines.
#: ''The '''taxicab distance''' between (0,0) and (3,4) is 7.''

